				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Cerys is preparing to lead the surviving tieflings onwards to Baldur’s Gate. Shocked to have survived the Shadow-Cursed Lands, she finds herself taking responsibility for the others - in Zevlor’s absence. It’s not a role she ever wanted, but somebody has to do it. She’s adjusting to a life without Zevlor, and briefly reflects on his surrender and presumed death."
